{"handle": "JFTrades_", "profile": {"username": "JFTrades_", "name": "Jeremy F", "avatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "followers": 7, "following": 9, "tweets": 39, "verified": true, "restId": "2008945880670613504"}, "history": [{"date": "2026-06-23", "followers": 6, "following": 9, "tweets": 39}, {"date": "2026-06-24", "followers": 6, "following": 9, "tweets": 39}, {"date": "2026-06-25", "followers": 7, "following": 9, "tweets": 39}, {"date": "2026-06-26", "followers": 7, "following": 9, "tweets": 39}, {"date": "2026-06-27", "followers": 7, "following": 9, "tweets": 39}, {"date": "2026-06-28", "followers": 7, "following": 9, "tweets": 39}], "posts": [{"id": "2008985283434332162", "text": "Hi, I’m Jeremy\n\nI started trading ICT concept in October but been trading for 5 years now. I’m using X to document my trades. I believe in truth and transparency. I’ll be posting up all my trades and explanations. Whether it is a win or a loss so I can learn better.\n\nI mainly trade NQ but I also trade other markets as well using this model:\n- Key level sweeps (Asia/London/PD highs & lows)\n- IFVG\n- SMT", "authorName": "Jeremy F", "authorUsername": "JFTrades_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 7, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 3, "retweetCount": 0, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 46, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-01-07T19:33:11+00:00", "hashtags": [], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/JFTrades_/status/2008985283434332162"}, {"id": "2022362094763708727", "text": "The importance of risk management. January was a hard month for me; it almost wiped me out. https://t.co/qN3fUa4xYg", "authorName": "Jeremy F", "authorUsername": "JFTrades_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 7, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 1, "retweetCount": 0,