012989200635765055"}, {"id": "2012989202820981027", "text": "- Daily Timeframe looks neutral/bearish\n- Bounced out of the Daily FVG\n- Daily EQH above \n- NQ consolidating and staying within the trend line", "authorName": "Jeremy F", "authorUsername": "JFTrades_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 7, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 1, "retweetCount": 0, "replyCount": 1, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 9, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-01-18T20:43:20+00:00", "hashtags": [], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/JFTrades_/status/2012989202820981027"}, {"id": "2012989208328020339", "text": "4H Timeframe\n\n- 4H trending down, making lower highs\n- #NQ within the 4G FVG and above the Daily FVG\n- Price needs to respect that Daily FVG if not we can see NQ crashing down https://t.co/4WgVmRDL0e", "authorName": "Jeremy F", "authorUsername": "JFTrades_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 7, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 2, "retweetCount": 0, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 8, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-01-18T20:43:21+00:00", "hashtags": ["NQ"], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/JFTrades_/status/2012989208328020339"}, {"id": "2011835086950273093", "text": "In trading, there is no such thing as a 100% win rate. You have to learn how to manage losses and risk. That is trading. Took a L today, still up big from yesterday. Not going to try anything else today. https://t.co/23BxhthN6L", "authorName": "Jeremy F", "authorUsername": "JFTrades_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 7, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 2, "retweetCount": 0, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 14, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-01-15T16:17:17+00:00", "hashtags": [], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/JFTrades_/status/2011835086950273093"}, {"id": "2011826304690139307", "text": "IFVG Trade of the Day:\n\n- #NQ broke down and created a Breaker Block. Low, High, Lower Low &amp; Higher High\n- Broke the 1M FVG \n- Target was Pre-Market high for 50 points. 1.5RR https://t.co/6mlhsddvTp", "authorName": "Jeremy F", "authorUsername": "JFTrades_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 7, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 1, "retweetCount": 0, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 15, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-01-15T15:42:23+00:00", "hashtags": ["NQ"], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/JFTrades_/status/2011826304690139307"}, {"id": "2011655183193755964", "text": "Live trade from today. #NQ #ICT https://t.co/CYLkifFCte", "authorName": "Jeremy F", "authorUsername": "JFTrades_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 7, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 2, "retweetCount": 1, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 21, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-01-15T04:22:25+00:00", "hashtags": ["NQ", "ICT"], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/JFTrades_/status/2011655183193755964"}, {"id": "2011482735538245700", "text": "IFVG Trade of the Day:\n\n- #NQ swept the PDL of last Thursday\n- Inversed the 1M FVG\n- Held the trendline up\n- TP 1 for me was 50 points, and I held the rest for TP 2 at the bottom of the 2M FVG\n- 2RR trade. A+ setup https://t.co/MXfKkMqQjJ", "authorName": "Jeremy F", "authorUsername": "JFTrades_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2008950608703684609/rtIPDXEL_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 7, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 1, "retweetCount": 0, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 17, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-01-14T16:57:10+00:00", "hashtags": ["NQ"], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x